NagiosCLI

`nagioscli` is a small curses-based nagios appliation. Once installed,
configure it by creating a ~/.nagioscli ini file like so:

[Identifier]
url=http://path/to/cgi-bin/status.cgi
username=nagiosadmin
password=foobar



INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install
